Task:
    Enter three integers a, b, c. Square the smallest number. Extract all values.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Solution:

    a=int(input("Input a: "))
    b=int(input("Input b: "))
    c=int(input("Input c: "))

    min=a

    if b<c:
        if b<min:
            min=b
            print("a= ", a)
            print("b= ", b**2)
            print("c= ", c)
        else:
            print("a= ", a**2)
            print("b= ", b)
            print("c= ", c)
    if c<b:
        if c<min:
            min=c
            print("a= ", a)
            print("b= ", b)
            print("c= ", c**2)
        else:
            print("a= ", a**2)
            print("b= ", b)
            print("c= ", c)

    if (a==b) and (b==c):
        print("All the numbers are equal (", min,")")
